# GitHub language detection (Linguist)
#
# This repository contains a legacy static HTML site (root index.html and the
# /about, /services, /team, /contact, /proof folders, plus /css and /js) that
# predates the Next.js application in /app. Those files inflate the HTML/CSS
# counts and obscure the real Next.js / TypeScript stack on GitHub.
#
# Marking them as vendored excludes them from the language statistics (and
# collapses them in diffs) without removing them from the repository.

/index.html linguist-vendored
/about/** linguist-vendored
/services/** linguist-vendored
/team/** linguist-vendored
/contact/** linguist-vendored
/proof/** linguist-vendored
/css/** linguist-vendored
/js/** linguist-vendored
